affix.java.effective.trackandfield
Interface TrackAndFieldCompetition

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractFieldCompetition, AbstractTrackCompetition, LongJumpCompetition
public interface TrackAndFieldCompetition

This interface defines methods that are applicable for any type of Track & Field competition. The two main branches will implement methods somewhat differently Track competitions use time measuring while Field competitions use length measuring Some competitions offer more than one attempt, some delivers result after a single performance
